        public java.util.List<java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.Object>> getConflictingDates()
        Description copied from interface: IntfDataRoomAllocation
        Get a list of all conflicting dates.
        That means courses in the same room, at the same time in the same semester
        Specified by:
        getConflictingDates in interface IntfDataRoomAllocation
        Returns:
        an ArrayList of HashMaps for each conflicting date.
        The HashMap has the following entries:
        "roomid" - the affected ID of the room
        "time" - the Integer of the affected time
        "day" - the Integer of the affected day
        "semester" - the String of the affected Semester
